# Proxy kiron.ai/buy-pock → BROK Bio-Age checkout (Caddy example)
#
# Deploy the Bio-Age web app to Vercel (or your host), then point
# kiron.ai/buy-pock at the same /buy-pock route.
#
# Option A — full app on bio-age subdomain, path proxy on kiron.ai:
#
# bio-age.kiron.ai {
#     reverse_proxy https://your-app.vercel.app
# }
#
# kiron.ai {
#     handle_path /buy-pock* {
#         reverse_proxy https://your-app.vercel.app
#     }
#     # ... rest of Kiron site
# }
#
# Option B — set env on Vercel:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_POCK_STRIPE_URL=https://kiron.ai/buy-pock
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://kiron.ai
#
# Stripe webhook endpoint (Vercel):
#   POST https://your-app.vercel.app/api/stripe/webhook